I've created a branch, but when I press refresh on branches in the CVS 
perspective, the branch tag does not appear.

The branch tag was visible in the CVS perspective this morning, but now it is 
gone. I don't know what I did to make the branch tag appear. It dissappeared 
when I did a refresh.

Some more information:

I have a couple of projects that I branched and they are are under a 
subdirectory in CVS. 

xpo/foo
xpo/foo2

"xpo" is not branched. I don't know if there is such a thing as a branched 
directory, or whether it was only files that could be branched.

"foo" and "foo2" are branched.


Here is a copy of the log, I don't know how much it contains that is relevant, 
but I'm including it anyway.

project).
